    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/korean-skincare-uk/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_ARTICLE&editorId=590173174029615750&sectionId=590173174079947398)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSeD_5BpRe_text","label":"ggSeD_5BpRe_text","default":"<p><a href=\"#gLdNijixX9\"><span style=\"color:#FFC5E1;\">Introduction</span></a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRtqxKFh4j_text","label":"ggRtqxKFh4j_text","default":"<p><a href=\"#gdRf3p8y1z\">The story behind JUMISO</a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDWYk8HtfY_text","label":"ggDWYk8HtfY_text","default":"<p><a href=\"#g5qhTA5e6X\">About the brand</a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggUqM5Vr3_s_text","label":"ggUqM5Vr3_s_text","default":"<p><a href=\"#gwXZvLyPZ2\">About the products</a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTyXNItrNY_text","label":"ggTyXNItrNY_text","default":"<p><a href=\"#gfjmgfzoUF\">Meet the newness</a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6iu2G1l1R_text","label":"gg6iu2G1l1R_text","default":"<p><a href=\"#geIziwjWKv\">Looking ahead</a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggA5hgLkFwW_text","label":"ggA5hgLkFwW_text","default":"<p><a href=\"#goUE24q9Y7\">Final thoughts</a></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsuc8uMOvV_text","label":"ggsuc8uMOvV_text","default":"<p><i>If you’re new to Korean skincare, there’s one brand you need to know: JUMISO. Known for playful packaging and skin-loving formulas, JUMISO was created to make your skin, and your day smile.</i></p><p><br><i>As one of the first brands we introduced to our site, JUMISO holds a special place in our collection. From early character-inspired designs to today’s cult-favorite essentials, the brand continues to deliver products people can’t get enough of.</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggoxIGOxvsy_text","label":"ggoxIGOxvsy_text","default":"The story behind JUMISO"},{"type":"html","id":"ggGJGclMkS2_text","label":"ggGJGclMkS2_text","default":"<p>We sat down with the CEO of <a href=\"$locationOrigin/collections/jumiso\"><span style=\"color:#FD76A9;\"><i>JUMISO</i></span></a> to learn more about the brand’s beginnings and inspiration.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeVwVUDs6h_text","label":"ggeVwVUDs6h_text","default":"Can you introduce yourself to our readers?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggc1G2yyyXw_text","label":"ggc1G2yyyXw_text","default":"<p>I’m Siheon Keum, co-founder of Jumiso. While I was a senior in university, my younger brother and I founded Jumiso in 2016.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzrF_XP6hm_text","label":"ggzrF_XP6hm_text","default":"What inspired you to start JUMISO, and what was the very first product you launched?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQTsl-3-T5_text","label":"ggQTsl-3-T5_text","default":"<p>At that time, Korean cosmetics exports were growing rapidly. As a student majoring in economics and international trade, I naturally became interested in products that performed well overseas.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>My father worked in the business of supplying cosmetic packaging materials, so I grew up surrounded by the beauty industry and learned how cosmetics were made and exported. Not many people remember it now, but our very first products were a set of five <a href=\"$locationOrigin/collections/sheet-masks\"><span style=\"color:#FD76A9;\"><i>sheet masks</i></span></a> featuring cute character designs.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZASM0AhLB_text","label":"ggZASM0AhLB_text","default":"About the brand"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTB6eHMDnM_text","label":"ggTB6eHMDnM_text","default":"What does “JUMISO” mean, and how does it reflect your philosophy?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggF94zXCbfL_text","label":"ggF94zXCbfL_text","default":"<p>When we created the brand, I wanted the name to carry a positive meaning every time people said it. I also wanted it to be a Korean word, so we chose one that means “smile.” Looking back, I sometimes think we could have picked a name that sounds more like a skincare brand but since people love it and remember it well, I think it turned out just fine.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggglochsxvl_text","label":"ggglochsxvl_text","default":"Why does K-Beauty stand out and how does JUMISO capture that uniqueness?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeXpe44Ure_text","label":"ggeXpe44Ure_text","default":"<p>Cosmetics are an emotional product — people often connect to them through <strong>feeling rather than logic</strong>. I think that emotional connection aligned perfectly with the global rise of <strong>K-culture</strong>, fueling the popularity of K-Beauty.</p><p><br>Korea’s “<strong>ppalli-ppalli</strong>” (quickly, quickly) culture also plays a role — our industries move fast, adapt quickly, and focus heavily on exports. Jumiso was never built just for the local market; from the beginning, we naturally looked outward.</p><p><br>At first, Jumiso didn’t attract much attention. I lacked experience and didn’t fully understand the market. But earlier this year, I began to think deeply about what makes us unique, and that’s when we developed the new concept of <strong>K-Derma</strong> — blending Korean skincare sensibilities with dermatological science. Once we started communicating that message clearly, the market began to respond.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKbto_euSn_text","label":"ggKbto_euSn_text","default":"About the products"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeq1b00F-p_text","label":"ggeq1b00F-p_text","default":"<p><i>All Day Vitamin line</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggig3OmIUu4_text","label":"ggig3OmIUu4_text","default":"<p><i>Waterfull line</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggShyIUfwdO_text","label":"ggShyIUfwdO_text","default":"<p>Niacinamide line</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_bAD4gIJv_text","label":"gg_bAD4gIJv_text","default":"<p><i>D-Panthenol line</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcKkN1Ncse_text","label":"ggcKkN1Ncse_text","default":"<p><i>Pore-Cleansing line</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggSqrxNsIJx_label","label":"ggSqrxNsIJx_label","default":"<p>SHOP JUMISO</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggifGE90O_f_text","label":"ggifGE90O_f_text","default":"Could you recommend a few Jumiso products for our readers who are new to the brand?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggW2jrR4Ukc_text","label":"ggW2jrR4Ukc_text","default":"<p>Without hesitation, I’d recommend our <a href=\"$locationOrigin/products/jumiso-niacinamide-20-serum\"><span style=\"color:#FD76A9;\"><i>Niacinamide 20 Serum</i></span></a>. We invested a tremendous amount of time in every stage, from concept planning and clinical testing to perfecting the texture.<br><br>Most serums on the market contain around <strong>10% Niacinamide</strong>, but we went beyond that to pioneer a <strong>20% formula</strong>. We worked hard to achieve both stability and strong functionality. While skincare results often depend on skin type, this serum truly delivers the core benefits of Niacinamide — brightening, balancing, and improving overall skin texture.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggQeZHvVdAj_text","label":"ggQeZHvVdAj_text","default":"What’s your own skincare routine like? Do you personally use Jumiso every day?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggsrGiTs3gu_text","label":"ggsrGiTs3gu_text","default":"<p>These days, the temperature difference between day and night in Korea is quite large, so I focus on oil control in the morning and hydration at night.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Recently, <strong>cleansing milk</strong> has become a trend in Korea. Since we launched our own cleansing milk, I’ve been using it daily. I try to test a wide range of new products — both our own and others on the market — to keep up with trends and understand how consumer needs are changing.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggcpbNuAHoj_text","label":"ggcpbNuAHoj_text","default":"Meet the newness: The Niacinamide 20 Serum and D-Panthenol line"},{"type":"html","id":"ggjj1Cg5lde_text","label":"ggjj1Cg5lde_text","default":"We’ve launched new JUMISO products, could you share more about how these products are developed and where the ideas come from?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRtyjGn6oe_text","label":"ggRtyjGn6oe_text","default":"<p>During a business trip to Malaysia, I visited several retail stores for market research. I noticed that Niacinamide-based products from various global brands were among the most popular items.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Later, I met with influencers to discuss which ingredients were trending, and again, <a href=\"$locationOrigin/collections/niacinamide\"><span style=\"color:#FD76A9;\"><i>Niacinamide</i></span></a> was the clear favorite. Most brands offered formulas with only 10% concentration, so we decided to push the limits and develop something new — a <strong>20% Niacinamide serum</strong>.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>There was internal hesitation at first — people worried it might be too strong. So we focused on <strong>reducing stickiness and improving comfort</strong>, spending eight months perfecting the formula. The result was worth it.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The idea for the <strong>D-Panthenol</strong> line came from a personal moment. When my baby developed a diaper rash, I bought a pharmacy ointment with Dexpanthenol. It inspired me to explore how we could bring that <strong>soothing, barrier-repairing</strong> ingredient into daily skincare.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gggZ3ShAwVA_label","label":"gggZ3ShAwVA_label","default":"See more"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnur9Xbxq3_label","label":"ggnur9Xbxq3_label","default":"See more"},{"type":"html","id":"gga1qD-4I8R_label","label":"gga1qD-4I8R_label","default":"See more"},{"type":"html","id":"ggklSXOjmJi_label","label":"ggklSXOjmJi_label","default":"See more"},{"type":"html","id":"gghzwOZXUqz_text","label":"gghzwOZXUqz_text","default":"Our customers are especially excited about the Niacinamide 20 Serum. Can you explain more about its benefits and why it has become such a fan favorite?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRuuusuU0B_text","label":"ggRuuusuU0B_text","default":"<p>We managed to capture both <strong>curiosity and concern</strong> at the same time. Customers were intrigued by a 20% Niacinamide serum but also worried it might be too strong. As real consumer reviews came in, those fears disappeared — and the product’s reputation spread quickly.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Ultimately, it all comes down to one simple truth: <strong>a good product speaks for itself</strong>. By staying true to function, understanding the market, and focusing on results, we achieved strong growth even with a modest marketing budget.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTA6kDfIDu_text","label":"ggTA6kDfIDu_text","default":"Looking ahead: The future of JUMISO"},{"type":"html","id":"gg7BEoqTQYl_text","label":"gg7BEoqTQYl_text","default":"What skincare trends are you most excited about right now, and how is Jumiso adapting to them?"},{"type":"html","id":"gg15j6-42P__text","label":"gg15j6-42P__text","default":"<p>After <a href=\"$locationOrigin/collections/oil-cleansers\"><span style=\"color:#FD76A9;\"><i>cleansing oils</i></span></a> and pack cleansers, we believe the next big thing is cleansing milk — and several brands, including ours, are already exploring this category.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLZL27Iq8S_text","label":"ggLZL27Iq8S_text","default":"What can fans look forward to from Jumiso in the future?"},{"type":"html","id":"ggmz-P2DFbb_text","label":"ggmz-P2DFbb_text","default":"<p>We hope people will continue to follow how we develop our unique vision of <strong>K-Derma</strong>. While European brands pioneered the derma category, our goal is to reinterpret it through a Korean lens — creating skincare that blends dermatological science with K-beauty innovation and accessibility.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBGWKX4pzx_text","label":"ggBGWKX4pzx_text","default":"Final thoughts"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRA4cODjof_text","label":"ggRA4cODjof_text","default":"<p>JUMISO is always innovating. Expect fun, effective, and skin-loving products inspired by the latest skincare trends. Fans can look forward to more cult favorites and approachable skincare routines that make taking care of your skin a joyful experience.</p>"}],
    "blocks": [{"type": "@app"}],
    "locales": {}
